@item Processing:
Manage collection repository binding on the chrooted jail for
@acronym{SSH} remote access.
@example
function JAIL_bind()
@{
  @dots{}
  mount --bind $MDTXHOME/cache $JAIL/var/cache
  mount --bind $CVSROOT $JAIL/var/lib/cvsroot
  @dots{}
@}
@end example
